ayoffs and those persistent divestiture rumors (I hear Lauder plans on keep=
ing its haircare brands, by the way), everyone at the GM Building is <em>re=
ally </em>talking about the =E2=80=9Cclusters=E2=80=9D=E2=80=94E.L.C.=E2=80=
