=99re no longer calling leads =E2=80=98executive group presidents,=E2=80=99=
=E2=80=9D said a person with knowledge of the matter. =E2=80=9CE.L.C. has t=
raditionally segmented their brands by tiers=E2=80=93=E2=80=93luxury
markets versus masstige, etcetera=E2=80=93=E2=80=93which is an old-fashione=
d way of looking at it, so segmenting by category is a =E2=80=98big change=
=E2=80=99 for them.=E2=80=9D</p></div>
